      "4": "eneken iakwb tou paidos mou kai israhl tou eklektou mou egw kalesw se tw onomati sou kai prosdexomai se su de ouk egnws me",
      "5": "oti egw kurios o qeos kai ouk estin eti plhn emou qeos kai ouk hdeis me",
      "6": "ina gnwsin oi apo anatolwn hliou kai oi apo dusmwn oti ouk estin plhn emou egw kurios o qeos kai ouk estin eti",
      "7": "egw o kataskeuasas fws kai poihsas skotos o poiwn eirhnhn kai ktizwn kaka egw kurios o qeos o poiwn tauta panta",
