      "23": "kai embalw auto eis tas ceiras twn adikhsantwn se kai twn tapeinwsantwn se oi eipan th yuch sou kuyon ina parelqwmen kai eqhkas isa th gh ta metafrena sou exw tois paraporeuomenois"
